item.description:
these episodes aren't available on disney+, so i tried finding these episodes. i ripped s01e18 on a season 1 dvd of tslozac (from @DearJohn) and found a russian dub on youtube (the channel is copyrighted outside of most central asian countries) (from https://www.youtube.com/@KanalDisneySeries). i also found s03e20 (don't remember how), and found a russian dub from the same youtube channel (from https://www.youtube.com/@KanalDisneySeries)

s01e18 also has latin spanish and brazilian dubs
